# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:4
translate Schinese findtj_522e252e:

    # "I'm really worried about TJ."
    "我真的很担心TJ。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:5
translate Schinese findtj_e5e0f975:

    # "He's a sensitive guy and, after a tongue-lashing like that from someone like Flynn.. I can't imagine what state he's in."
    "他生性敏感，而在被Flynn如此辱骂后...我很难想象他现在是怎样的心情。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:6
translate Schinese findtj_6c7f7ec2:

    # "I don't see him anywhere as I scan the area, but I do see some trees and bushes further up along the riverbank."
    "扫过四周，我并没能发现他的身影，不过河岸沿线的树木与灌木清晰地映入了我的眼帘。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:7
translate Schinese findtj_416c7d34:

    # "Since there's really no other place to hide, I assume that's where he's at."
    "我想他可能在那儿，毕竟附近没有其他可以躲藏的地方了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:10
translate Schinese findtj_8911b009:

    # "Sure enough, I see him immediately. He's sitting down, knees drawn up with his arms folded on top of them."
    "不出所料，我立马发现了他。他两腿蜷曲，抱住膝盖，蹲坐在地上。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:11
translate Schinese findtj_140343c8:

    # "He's got his forehead resting on top of his arms, staring down at the sand between his legs."
    "他把前额搁在胳膊上，透过双腿看向地上的泥沙。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:12
translate Schinese findtj_5f808aba:

    # "I stand there for a moment, wondering if it will just be better to leave him alone."
    "我在那儿站了一会儿，思考着让他一个人呆着是否会更好。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:13
translate Schinese findtj_6bdda4bd:

    # "After a few seconds I finally decide to sit down next to him, cross-legged."
    "不过几秒钟后，我决定在他身旁盘腿坐下。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:15
translate Schinese findtj_17c746ee:

    # "His ears flick in my direction and he turns his head to the left, away from me."
    "他的耳朵向我的方向跳动着，头却偏向一旁。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:16
translate Schinese findtj_a24a26d6:

    # "I notice a few wet spots between his feet."
    "我发现他双腿之间的地面上有些湿润。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:17
translate Schinese findtj_a03241ec:

    # "Maybe he just wants to be left alone now?"
    "也许我应该让他自己呆一会儿？"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:20
translate Schinese findtj_2c82dd2d:

    # "I decide that I need to break the silence."
    "我决定打破沉默。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:21
translate Schinese findtj_9f246c23:

    # m "\"Heeey, TJ...\""
    m "\"嘿，TJ...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:22
translate Schinese findtj_52be0157:

    # "He doesn't say anything, or move."
    "他沉默着，一动也不动。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:23
translate Schinese findtj_e0983fb0:

    # m "\"You know how Flynn is...he's a dick.\""
    m "\"你知道Flynn...他就是个混蛋。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:24
translate Schinese findtj_8336c758:

    # "Again, silence."
    "仍是沉默。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:25
translate Schinese findtj_8eb3d331:

    # m "\"Everyone knows he's a dick. No one's mad at you.\""
    m "\"大家都知道他是个混蛋。没人会生你的气的。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:26
translate Schinese findtj_ee8b3fe7:

    # "He does move, then, sliding his legs out straight and leaning back on his paws."
    "他这才有了动作，伸直了伸腿，用双手把头抱住。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:27
translate Schinese findtj_18401036:

    # "He's still looking away from me, rubbing his face on his shoulder."
    "他还是没有看着我，而是用肩膀蹭了蹭脸颊。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:28
translate Schinese findtj_20e9fb5e:

    # m "\"You wanna go back and eat?\""
    m "\"你想回去吃东西么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:29
translate Schinese findtj_97f0c146:

    # "Finally..."
    "终于..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:31
translate Schinese findtj_1ef278dc:

    # "I decide to let TJ talk when he's ready."
    "还是等TJ平复下来后再跟他说话吧。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:32
translate Schinese findtj_9821a669:

    # "In the meantime, I pick up a dry twig and start toying with it, snapping it in half, then snapping the other halves in half."
    "与此同时，我捡起一根树枝把玩着，一段一段地折成两半。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:33
translate Schinese findtj_2486b583:

    # "I can see that his ears are still swiveled in my direction, probably wondering what the hell I'm doing."
    "我能看见他的耳朵仍转向我的方向，大概是在想我在搞什么鬼吧。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:34
translate Schinese findtj_7f72af2c:

    # "I think I'm getting on his nerves because finally he talks."
    "或许是招惹到他了吧，他终于开口说话了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:35
translate Schinese findtj_e233567e:

    # t "\"What do you want, Chase?\""
    t "\"你到底想干什么，Chase？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:36
translate Schinese findtj_e476235b:

    # "I throw the pieces of the twig into the river."
    "我把一截树枝扔进河里。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:37
translate Schinese findtj_e0e952cf:

    # m "\"Just wondering where you went. You wanna go back and eat?\""
    m "\"只是在想你跑哪儿去了。你想回去吃东西么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:38
translate Schinese findtj_564d4d01:

    # t "\"No.\""
    t "\"不想。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:39
translate Schinese findtj_1c084dfc:

    # "We sit there for a while longer as I watch the twig pieces float down the river."
    "我们仍坐在那儿，而我看着树枝顺流而下。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:40
translate Schinese findtj_97f0c146_1:

    # "Finally..."
    "终于..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:42
translate Schinese findtj_36225632:

    # "Definitely not worth it."
    "我没必要这么做。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:43
translate Schinese findtj_edabcd71:

    # "I really don't wanna make things worse than they already are."
    "我不想把事情搅和得更糟。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:44
translate Schinese findtj_af995e38:

    # "I'm not exactly graceful with this sort of thing, especially with TJ."
    "我不太擅长处理这种事儿，尤其是扯上TJ的时候。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:45
translate Schinese findtj_be68f68b:

    # "For now, I should probably just go talk to one of the others."
    "我想我现在还是去跟其他人谈谈吧。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:57
translate Schinese findtj_1f6d77b0:

    # t "\"I can't believe he did that...in front of everyone.\""
    t "\"我不敢相信，他居然当着...所有人的面做出这种事。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:58
translate Schinese findtj_4c489731:

    # "I'm not sure what to say, so I stay quiet."
    "我不知道该说些什么好，于是保持沉默。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:59
translate Schinese findtj_45c763fa:

    # "After a minute, TJ finally turns his head, looking into the river."
    "几分钟后，TJ终于转过头去看向河面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:60
translate Schinese findtj_a2318972:

    # "The wind picks up, reflections from the river highlighting motes of dust that swirl up around us."
    "风开始刮起，河面的反射映照出我们周围飞舞的尘沙。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:61
translate Schinese findtj_2057d6ed:

    # "His face fur is a bit mussed up, spiked up in a few places from being wet."
    "他脸上的毛发变得杂乱，几处毛发因被打湿而拧成一团。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:62
translate Schinese findtj_a80314ff:

    # "It's an unusual sight to see his fur unkempt."
    "我不常见他这样蓬头垢面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:63
translate Schinese findtj_45176cc0:

    # t "\"I mean, what the ffh—\""
    t "\"我是说，到底他m—\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:64
translate Schinese findtj_d50ed3bd:

    # t "\"...what the heck?\""
    t "\"...到底发生了什么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:65
translate Schinese findtj_3e95783d:

    # "TJ; unable to curse even though it would probably be the best thing for him."
    "TJ；尽管骂出来会好受很多，但他还是做不到。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:66
translate Schinese findtj_1045cb67:

    # "He adjusts his legs to sit cross-legged, like me, and wipes his face again."
    "他像我一样盘腿并坐，又擦了擦脸。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:67
translate Schinese findtj_10fa8037:

    # t "\"D—did you know...what he was talking about?\""
    t "\"你—你知道...他刚才说的是什么吗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:68
translate Schinese findtj_76c2507a:

    # "I take in a breath, unsure about how I should approach this."
    "我深吸一口气，不知该怎么处理这个问题。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:69
translate Schinese findtj_2014df1e:

    # m "\"I {i}think{/i} so?\""
    m "\"我想我{i}知道{/i}吧？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:70
translate Schinese findtj_633b1ece:

    # "TJ's ears lower."
    "TJ的耳朵垂得更低了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:71
translate Schinese findtj_fa843525:

    # m "\"Listen, no one else thinks anything happened. We were so little, especially you.\""
    m "\"听着，我们之外没人意识到发生了什么。那时我们还小，尤其是你。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:72
translate Schinese findtj_76e6c71a:

    # m "\"I mean, I can't believe he's doing this...\""
    m "\"我的意思是，我还是不敢相信他居然干出这种事...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:73
translate Schinese findtj_006a4484:

    # "I trace a claw through the dirt, drawing some wavy patterns as I try to make sense of all this myself."
    "我用手划过泥土，画出波浪的图案，思考着该如何跟他解释。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:74
translate Schinese findtj_aea7a843:

    # m "\"I think it's just because he was such good friends with Sydney, and he just wants more than the truth.\""
    m "\"大概是因为他和Sydney是交情甚好的朋友吧，他也只是想知道在表面的真相之下到底隐藏了什么。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:75
translate Schinese findtj_aac778f4:

    # "I look sideways at TJ."
    "我侧目看着TJ。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:76
translate Schinese findtj_219bc6db:

    # "He's just sitting there, looking at the ground."
    "他只是坐在那儿，眼神瞟向地面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:77
translate Schinese findtj_b42aa832:

    # m "\"And I guess you were the only one that saw him...saw what happened...so he only has you to go after.\""
    m "\"而且你应该是唯一一个看到了他...看到发生什么了的人...因此他只能以你为目标。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:78
translate Schinese findtj_07eb5da3:

    # t "\"I saw him drown.\""
    t "\"我亲眼看着他淹死了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:79
translate Schinese findtj_9b7b2a9c:

    # "I don't say anything, but I feel myself cringe inwardly."
    "我没说话，却感觉内心惶恐不安。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:80
translate Schinese findtj_cad70052:

    # "Pretty soon tears are running down TJ's face, but he doesn't bother to wipe them away."
    "眼泪很快顺着TJ的脸庞流了下来，但他没有擦去泪水。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:81
translate Schinese findtj_feec1422:

    # "He's not just sad, though; he's angry. I hear it in his voice as he goes on."
    "他的内心不仅含有悲伤；还有愤怒。我听着他的声音继续说下去。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:82
translate Schinese findtj_f5d85ddb:

    # t "\"I saw Sydney drown and Flynn thinks he's the only one that hurts?\""
    t "\"我亲眼看着Sydney溺水而死，而Flynn以为他是唯一一个因此受伤的人？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:83
translate Schinese findtj_bead0425:

    # t "\"He thinks that he's the only one that feels like he's in a nightmare?\""
    t "\"他真以为他是唯一一个把一切当作噩梦的人么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:84
translate Schinese findtj_a5840dd7:

    # t "\"Well maybe...\""
    t "\"也许...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:85
translate Schinese findtj_c0a4efd1:

    # "His voice cracks and he looks away from me again, wiping at his face."
    "他的声音颤抖起来，再次转过头去，擦拭着自己的脸。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:86
translate Schinese findtj_4e72e1d8:

    # t "\"...Maybe I haven't told him everything because I don't want him to have those images in his head.\""
    t "\"...也许我没告诉他一切是因为我不想让他日夜想起这些可怕的事吧。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:87
translate Schinese findtj_9c2e69f6:

    # "TJ takes a moment to steady his voice, working to get his breathing back to normal."
    "TJ花了些时间平稳他的声音，尽力让呼吸重归正常。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:88
translate Schinese findtj_5b697acf:

    # t "\"I just...I just wish I could go back to that day.\""
    t "\"我...我只想希望自己可以回到那一天。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:89
translate Schinese findtj_3c6b2cbe:

    # m "\"TJ...there's nothing you could have done.\""
    m "\"TJ...你什么也做不了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:90
translate Schinese findtj_0f0fa673:

    # "I know my words are meaningless crap, and I hate myself for saying them."
    "我知道自己的话毫无意义，我也讨厌自己说出这样的话。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:91
translate Schinese findtj_3fd3cab1:

    # "But I have to say something."
    "但我得说些什么。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:92
translate Schinese findtj_921f04ac:

    # m "\"Not one of us would have been able to do anything if we were there.\""
    m "\"就算回到过去，我们也什么都做不了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:93
translate Schinese findtj_2f65c229:

    # t "\"You would have.\""
    t "\"你们应该做些什么的。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:94
translate Schinese findtj_63033175:

    # m "\"Well...\""
    m "\"好吧...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:95
translate Schinese findtj_56fc07d7:

    # t "\"Besides, I already know I couldn't have saved him on my own. That isn't what...\""
    t "\"而且我知道仅靠我一个人的力量救不了他。但这不是...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:96
translate Schinese findtj_df4ce35e:

    # "TJ takes a moment to wipe his face again and when he's done he doesn't go on."
    "TJ又花了些时间擦拭着脸，不过他没有再继续说下去。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:97
translate Schinese findtj_42c52f4c:

    # "We sit in silence for a long while after that, and I adjust myself so that I can lean back against a rock behind me."
    "在那之后，我们坐在那儿，沉默了很长一段时间，我调整着坐姿，让自己靠在身后的石头上。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:98
translate Schinese findtj_6cd58a41:

    # "I pat the ground."
    "我拍了拍地面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:99
translate Schinese findtj_862d2574:

    # m "\"Sit next to me, Teej.\""
    m "\"坐我旁边来，Teej。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:100
translate Schinese findtj_9779a7de:

    # "He's calmed down for the most part and, after a moment, he does crawl over to sit by me."
    "他似乎平静了不少，过了一会儿，挪着身子坐到我身旁。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:102
translate Schinese findtj_105a3351:

    # "I pick up a few pebbles and toss them into the river."
    "我捡起一些鹅卵石扔进河里。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:103
translate Schinese findtj_41bf9197:

    # m "\"Remember when we used to call it Seesaw River?\""
    m "\"你还记得我们叫它跷板湖么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:104
translate Schinese findtj_d825f483:

    # t "\"Yeah...\""
    t "\"嗯...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:105
translate Schinese findtj_7e7b95d0:

    # "He leaves it at that, so I drop it."
    "他这样回答，于是我也放弃了这个话题。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:106
translate Schinese findtj_5ed07854:

    # "I rest my head back and close my eyes, only then realizing how tired I am."
    "我把头靠在石头上，闭着眼，只能感受到全身的疲惫。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:107
translate Schinese findtj_02b3eaba:

    # "In some way, I can see why Flynn is so suspicious, or at least why he believes there's more to the story."
    "某种程度上，我也能理解为什么Flynn如此怀疑了，至少明白为什么他敢肯定这故事背后还有所隐藏。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:108
translate Schinese findtj_33547e09:

    # "There clearly is."
    "肯定有所隐藏。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:109
translate Schinese findtj_7c74d204:

    # "But while I do want TJ to tell me more about what happened, I could never bring myself to ask him."
    "但就算我想让TJ告诉我到底发生了什么，我也没办法直接开口询问。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:110
translate Schinese findtj_47b4405a:

    # "I honestly feel that if I ever want to help him with his past, I should probably come to terms with it myself."
    "诚然，如果我想的话，我只能独自一人帮助TJ解决过去的回忆。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:111
translate Schinese findtj_2ae85c82:

    # "I crinkle my brow, toying with the idea of going back..."
    "我皱起眉，有些随便地考虑起回到过去的这个主意..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:112
translate Schinese findtj_c01d44f3:

    # "It's something I actively avoid thinking about. We all do."
    "我不想回想起那些事。我们所有人都不想。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:113
translate Schinese findtj_1182c12c:

    # "But like Jenna said, maybe talking about it, {i}thinking{/i} about it, might actually help."
    "不过就像Jenna所说，多谈谈，多{i}想想{/i}，也许会有帮助。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:114
translate Schinese findtj_41684e38:

    # "I dig my fingers into the pebbles on either side of me."
    "我把手指插进两旁的鹅卵石堆里。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:115
translate Schinese findtj_4e928379:

    # "The images come in a quick flurry, like someone cycling through a View-Master too fast."
    "像是在三维魔景机中快速循环一般，记忆的画面不断在我脑海中闪过。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:121
translate Schinese findtj_84d1ebb7:

    # "The sky is getting cloudy, the air crisp - autumn."
    "天空渐渐挂上了云朵，空气中弥漫着清新的味道...那是秋天的时节。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:122
translate Schinese findtj_3979329c:

    # "TJ sitting in a daze, Jenna running back to town, Flynn pulling me into the water..."
    "TJ在一旁呆坐，Jenna一路跑回镇上，Flynn把我推入水中..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:123
translate Schinese findtj_fa659190:

    # "...Me, grabbing onto neck scruff, pulling back to shore..."
    "...而我抓住颈部的毛发，把自己拉回岸上..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:124
translate Schinese findtj_b52b1245:

    # "Carl sitting on a rock, bawling, Leo starts trying to do compressions..."
    "Carl坐在岩石上大叫着，而Leo正准备做心脏复苏..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:125
translate Schinese findtj_9d91d735:

    # "And Sydney.. Sydney just stares."
    "还有Sydney...Sydney只是盯着。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:126
translate Schinese findtj_5551218a:

    # "Sirens, the helicopter rotors, adults everywhere."
    "警笛的鸣响，直升机的旋翼，到处都是成年人。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:127
translate Schinese findtj_063a1752:

    # "I'm home, mom's holding me. Dad puts on my favorite movie. I watch."
    "我在家里，妈妈抱着我。爸爸放着我最喜欢的电影。而我看着。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:128
translate Schinese findtj_bdd376b1:

    # "But still.. Sydney stares."
    "不过...Sydney仍只是盯着。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:134
translate Schinese findtj_9e9cda41:

    # "I open my eyes again and the world is blurred. The light reflecting off the river makes me squint."
    "我再次睁开眼，眼前的世界一片模糊。河面反射的光线使我虚起了眼。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:135
translate Schinese findtj_a6251de6:

    # "I rub my eyes with the back of my paw and it comes away wet."
    "我用手背揉了揉眼睛，已经湿润了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:136
translate Schinese findtj_bf690923:

    # "My chest hurts, and so does my head, throbbing and buzzing."
    "我的胸口一阵闷痛，头也疼痛起来，悖动着嗡嗡作响。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:137
translate Schinese findtj_f51f84c8:

    # "I look over and, luckily for me, TJ is leaning back with his eyes closed like I was."
    "我看过去，还好，TJ也像我刚才一样闭着眼向后靠着。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:138
translate Schinese findtj_41e5b952:

    # "If revisiting that day is so horrible for me, I can't imagine what it's like for him."
    "如果说那时的回忆对我来说过于可怕，那我很难想象他是怎么想的。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:139
translate Schinese findtj_41d692e2:

    # "I decide right then and there that I'm not going to press TJ on what happened."
    "我决定还是别逼着TJ告诉我那件事了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:140
translate Schinese findtj_fa530a76:

    # "If he wants to tell me more, he'll do it on his own accord."
    "如果他真有这个意思，他会自愿告诉我的吧。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:141
translate Schinese findtj_08d938fc:

    # "I kind of want to swim again, but at the same time I don't."
    "我有些希望再去游个泳，同时又不太想去。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:142
translate Schinese findtj_d8b468ff:

    # "That day really fucked up my view about water."
    "那一天真的搞砸了我对水的看法。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:143
translate Schinese findtj_4564d8fd:

    # t "\"He's ruined the whole trip...\""
    t "\"他毁了整个旅程...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:144
translate Schinese findtj_e898be33:

    # "TJ speaks suddenly, and I look over at him."
    "TJ突然开口了，我看向他。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:145
translate Schinese findtj_7aa85cdd:

    # m "\"Flynn? No he hasn't.\""
    m "\"Flynn？不，他没有。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:146
translate Schinese findtj_f46b236b:

    # "TJ does finally look at me, then, and I'm struck by how disheveled and sad he looks."
    "TJ终于看向我，他凌乱而悲伤的样子让我有些惊讶。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:147
translate Schinese findtj_742a0760:

    # "I feel anger bloom in my chest, all of it directed at Flynn."
    "我感到愤怒在我心中燃起——全都是指向Flynn的愤怒。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:148
translate Schinese findtj_1c9f33c0:

    # "What a selfish prick, thinking he had the right to ruin everyone's good time just because he felt like shit."
    "真是个自私的混蛋，他凭什么因为自己不爽就毁掉所有人享受美好的时光。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:149
translate Schinese findtj_b3ce1dae:

    # "If he were here right now I'm pretty sure I'd punch him right in the gut."
    "如果他现在在我面前，我一定会胖揍他一顿。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:150
translate Schinese findtj_26f82278:

    # m "\"Listen, we don't all need to hang out to have fun. We had fun at the park with just you, me, and Carl, remember?\""
    m "\"听着，我们没必要所有人一起出来玩。在游乐园的时候，你，我和Carl三个人也玩得很开心，还记得么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:151
translate Schinese findtj_0f833954:

    # m "\"If Flynn wants to be a douchebag then let him, we'll do our own thing.\""
    m "\"如果Flynn想做个混蛋，那就让他去吧，我们可以自己做自己的事情。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:154
translate Schinese findtj_51b58ce7:

    # "TJ sniffs and I see his tufted ears perk up a little."
    "TJ抽泣着，他的耳簇有些抬起。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:155
translate Schinese findtj_54cd158b:

    # m "\"Didn't you want to go hike the trail?\""
    m "\"你不是想沿着小径登山吗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:157
translate Schinese findtj_629e9ecb:

    # "He smiles at that and looks at me."
    "他看着我笑了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:158
translate Schinese findtj_d4ec207b:

    # t "\"You didn't want to hike, I could tell.\""
    t "\"你不想去登山，我看得出来。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:159
translate Schinese findtj_b91092c0:

    # "I grin."
    "我咧嘴笑着。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:160
translate Schinese findtj_2198ec83:

    # m "\"That's 'cuz it's so friggin' hot! But seriously, we didn't come here to lay in a motel all week.\""
    m "\"那是因为外面太他妈热了！不过说真的，我们来这儿的确不是为了整个星期都蹲在旅馆里。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:162
translate Schinese findtj_791d2ede:

    # t "\"And we can bring water! Just dump it on yourself every half-hour.\""
    t "\"我们可以把水带上！你每半个小时用水淋一下自己就好了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:163
translate Schinese findtj_ddd8bde5:

    # t "\"That's how I manage, along with taking plenty of breaks.\""
    t "\"我是这么打算，而且还得多停下来歇会儿。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:164
translate Schinese findtj_1e833196:

    # "TJ leans back and spreads his legs out."
    "TJ叉开腿向后靠去。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:165
translate Schinese findtj_ba0e2b13:

    # "I can see he's starting to get excited at the prospect of hiking, and that makes me feel better."
    "看着他因可以登山而逐渐兴奋起来，我的心情也好了不少。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:166
translate Schinese findtj_49b4a4af:

    # m "\"Well, if {i}you're{/i} able to do it, I guess I shouldn't complain.\""
    m "\"好吧，如果{i}你能{/i}这么做的话，我想我也没什么可抱怨的了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:167
translate Schinese findtj_522d7a14:

    # "I look over his fluffy form which, by itself, is enough to make me sweat even more than I am already."
    "光是看着他毛发旺盛的样子就足以让我热得冒汗—虽然我已经在流汗了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:168
translate Schinese findtj_9ab7ce6d:

    # m "\"You know, I always thought you'd go back after you graduated high school.\""
    m "\"你知道么，我一直以为你高中毕业以后就会回去。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:169
translate Schinese findtj_98cd4c83:

    # t "\"Hm?\""
    t "\"嗯？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:170
translate Schinese findtj_48a4a469:

    # m "\"The Great White North.\""
    m "\"枫叶之国。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:171
translate Schinese findtj_9761ba1d:

    # "I say it dramatically, nodding upwards as if that's where it is."
    "我夸张地说，同时用头指向上方，好像那就是它所在的地方一样。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:172
translate Schinese findtj_8778a158:

    # m "\"Your parents did.\""
    m "\"你的父母曾住的地方。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:173
translate Schinese findtj_065370bd:

    # "TJ's family moved to Echo when he was only six from a small town called Wasatchua."
    "TJ的家人在他六岁时从一个叫瓦萨奇亚的小镇搬到了回音镇来。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:174
translate Schinese findtj_6b150f35:

    # "His dad got a job in Echo to survey the land, or do something with the wildlife...I can't remember exactly what it was."
    "他的父亲在回音镇找到了一份工作，调查土地情况还是与野生动物打交道什么的...我记不清到底是什么了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:175
translate Schinese findtj_30e7ad4f:

    # t "\"Oh, well...I don't really remember it, but I might after I graduate. They have some things up there that sound really nice.\""
    t "\"哦，嗯...我不太记了，也许我毕业后会回去吧。那里有些东西听起来很不错。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:176
translate Schinese findtj_770d3baf:

    # m "\"Free healthcare?\""
    m "\"免费医疗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:177
translate Schinese findtj_6188ec73:

    # t "\"Ha, that I guess...and snow.\""
    t "\"哈，我想是的...还有雪。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:178
translate Schinese findtj_5d24b219:

    # "For a moment I wonder if snow is to a lynx as water is to an otter."
    "有那么一会儿，我在想雪对山猫来说是否像水对水獭一样重要。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:179
translate Schinese findtj_56a3593f:

    # "A lot of snow did sound kind of exciting to me, though. Here we'd be lucky to see a single dusting of it a year."
    "听到能看见满世界的雪确实会让我很兴奋。毕竟在这里一年下来也飘不了几片雪花。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:180
translate Schinese findtj_e2980d92:

    # t "\"Sooo, you're serious about hiking with me?\""
    t "\"所以，你真的要跟我一起去登山吗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:181
translate Schinese findtj_2680c34e:

    # m "\"Of course! I'm gonna bring some of my equipment, too. I think I wanna get some shots of the canyon.\""
    m "\"当然！我也会把设备带来，我想拍一些峡谷的照片。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:182
translate Schinese findtj_da2fb33f:

    # t "\"Okay!\""
    t "\"没问题！\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:183
translate Schinese findtj_13d0fd8b:

    # "He waggles his furry feet back and forth, and I hide a grin at his enthusiasm."
    "他晃悠着他毛茸的脚，他的热情使我差点笑了起来。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:184
translate Schinese findtj_f227aa49:

    # t "\"Alright, so we're going to have to get up around six.\""
    t "\"那好，所以我们六点左右就得起床。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:185
translate Schinese findtj_89357ba6:

    # m "\"Oh...\""
    m "\"噢...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:186
translate Schinese findtj_8a4722d0:

    # t "\"I want to be able to make it to the canyon for lunch where we can rest for an hour or two, then—\""
    t "\"我想走到峡谷去，在那儿我们可以吃午餐，顺便休息一两个小时，然后—\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:187
translate Schinese findtj_11b2fc6b:

    # "You can tell how excited TJ is by how much he talks."
    "从TJ口若悬河的样子，你完全可以看出他有多么兴奋。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:188
translate Schinese findtj_f487e4a0:

    # "Well, if anyone's good at planning things out at a ridiculously meticulous level, it's TJ."
    "好吧，如果有人能把这种事情计划得滴水不漏，那绝对是TJ了。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:189
translate Schinese findtj_f5390709:

    # "We sit there for another 20 minutes or so and just talk, mostly about school and what our plans are once we graduate."
    "我们坐在那儿又聊了大概20分钟左右，谈论的话题几乎都是学校和我们毕业后的计划。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:190
translate Schinese findtj_5f18077e:

    # "I promise TJ that we'll meet up again, before I do."
    "我向TJ保证，我们会在毕业之前见面的。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:191
translate Schinese findtj_aa4a7b01:

    # "That's when I get a text from Jenna asking where we are. I stand up, brushing off my pants before reaching down to help TJ up."
    "就在那时，我收到了Jenna的短信，她问我们现在在哪儿。我站起来，掸掉裤子上的灰尘，然后伸手把TJ拉了起来。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:192
translate Schinese findtj_d230817f:

    # m "\"Welp, we better go back. Guess they're all wondering where we are.\""
    m "\"好了，我们该回去了。他们估计还在想我们跑哪儿去了吧。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:197
translate Schinese findtj_77791319:

    # "When we get back, everything's packed up and in the van, along with Carl and Jenna."
    "当我们回来时，所有的东西都打包好放在货车里了，Carl和Jenna也坐在后面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:198
translate Schinese findtj_9f8310a8:

    # "Leo's leaning against the van, waiting for us, his paws in his pockets."
    "Leo把爪子插在口袋里，靠在货车上等着我们。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:200
translate Schinese findtj_325e976d:

    # "He looks at me, then over at TJ, obviously trying to gauge his mood."
    "他看了看我，又看了看TJ，显然是在打量他的情绪。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:201
translate Schinese findtj_285b057a:

    # l "\"...Everything good?\""
    l "\"...一切还好吗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:202
translate Schinese findtj_01e59cae:

    # t "\"Yeah.\""
    t "\"嗯。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:203
translate Schinese findtj_689c2806:

    # "TJ answers before I can, and whether or not he actually is okay, he sounds happy enough."
    "TJ抢在我开口之前回答了他，而且不管他现在是否真的没事，他听起来非常的开心。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:204
translate Schinese findtj_e5f75a54:

    # l "\"Well, alright then.\""
    l "\"嗯，那好吧。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:206
translate Schinese findtj_d2507065:

    # "We get in the van at that point, no one saying anything as we make the short drive back to the motel."
    "我们上了车，在回旅馆的一路上都没有人说话。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:211
translate Schinese findtj_dbb16dbb:

    # "As we get out Leo tells us all that he's going to have a word with Flynn and, despite the spoiled afternoon, we still had stuff to do over the week."
    "当我们下车时，Leo告诉我们说他会和Flynn好好谈一谈的，尽管下午有点扫兴，但我们这周还有不少事情要做。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:212
translate Schinese findtj_af6dbb4b:

    # "I'm not too convinced myself that that will happen. I am convinced that it's gonna be awkward as fuck if we do."
    "我不太相信他们真能好好谈谈。我只相信如果我们真这么做了，一定会非常尴尬。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:213
translate Schinese findtj_e345e5d3:

    # "Leo leaves for work at that point, though Carl does end up coming in with us to the motel room."
    "接着Leo就去上班了，而Carl最后还是跟着我们一块进了旅馆的房间。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:216
translate Schinese findtj_c832c315:

    # "The rest of the day is pretty uneventful; we watch a few movies then go to the diner for dinner."
    "那天剩下的时光相当平静，我们先是看了几部电影，然后去餐厅吃饭。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:217
translate Schinese findtj_a4881b58:

    # "Afterwards we just sit in the room and talk, Carl filling us in on how things have been in the town over the past three years."
    "随后我们就坐在房间里聊天，Carl给我们讲述了镇上过去三年的情况。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:218
translate Schinese findtj_1115ff98:

    # "It's not long before the conversation drifts back to Flynn and his outburst."
    "没过多久，话题又回到了Flynn和他发火的事上。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:220
translate Schinese findtj_a482001b:

    # c "\"I think he's just antsy 'cuz he's realizing how shitty it's been without you guys.\""
    c "\"我想他现在一定很不安，毕竟他意识到了没有你们的日子是多么糟糕。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:221
translate Schinese findtj_fd251563:

    # c "\"Trust me, he's already kicking himself for it right now.\""
    c "\"相信我，他现在一定已经后悔了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:223
translate Schinese findtj_eeb55409:

    # j "\"Even if he is it doesn't mean anything unless he apologizes.\""
    j "\"即便他这么想也没有任何意义，他必须道歉。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:224
translate Schinese findtj_422f6365:

    # c "\"Aww, you know how he is, Jenna. He's sorry even if he won't say it.\""
    c "\"啊，你知道他是个什么样的人，Jenna。即使他说不出口，但他的内心也一定十分歉疚。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:225
translate Schinese findtj_0da6b2c4:

    # j "\"I don't care, he's going to have to realize that none of us have to put up with him anymore.\""
    j "\"我不在乎，他会意识到我们再也不需要忍受他了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:227
translate Schinese findtj_8b0fd080:

    # t "\"Hey! Why don't we all get some ice cream? I've been wanting to go to Ray's ever since we got here.\""
    t "\"嘿！我们为什么不去吃点冰淇淋呢？从来到这儿开始，我就一直想去雷氏甜品看看。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:228
translate Schinese findtj_5a27a9f8:

    # "It's hard to tell if TJ is just trying to change the subject, or actually wants ice cream...probably both."
    "很难说TJ是想转移话题，还是真的想吃冰淇淋...可能两者兼而有之。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:229
translate Schinese findtj_b4d92777:

    # c "\"Heh, if you wanna drive half an hour to Payton, sure.\""
    c "\"嘿，如果你想开半小时的车到沛顿市去，那就没问题。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:231
translate Schinese findtj_c126d37e:

    # t "\"What, why?\""
    t "\"什么，为什么？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:232
translate Schinese findtj_fbf1cb17:

    # c "\"They moved it there. It sucks, I haven't had their rocky road for a year now.\""
    c "\"他们把店搬到了那儿去了。烦死了，我已经有一年没吃过他们的石板街冰淇淋了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:234
translate Schinese findtj_d2e68fea:

    # t "\"Awww...\""
    t "\"唔...\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:235
translate Schinese findtj_1a7202d9:

    # j "\"Well, let's just stop by when we go to Payton next. I assume we aren't staying in Echo for the rest of the trip.\""
    j "\"好吧，我们下一次去沛顿的时候可以顺便去看看。我想我接下来的应该不会再呆在回音镇了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:237
translate Schinese findtj_6b4f3e0a:

    # t "\"Ooh! Chase, can you take us?\""
    t "\"哦！Chase，你能带上我们吗？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:238
translate Schinese findtj_133c7699:

    # "I just smile at him from my spot on the couch."
    "我只是坐在沙发上，对他微笑。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:239
translate Schinese findtj_b778d267:

    # m "\"Sure, why not?\""
    m "\"当然，为什么不呢？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:240
translate Schinese findtj_e40903e0:

    # t "\"Yes! I love the cookie dough.\""
    t "\"太好了！我喜欢曲奇饼。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:241
translate Schinese findtj_6daa35e7:

    # t "\"What about you, Jenna?\""
    t "\"你呢，Jenna？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:242
translate Schinese findtj_abef1f99:

    # "Jenna's busy looking at her phone."
    "Jenna正忙着看她的手机。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:243
translate Schinese findtj_be135aad:

    # j "\"Hmm? Oh, well I've always enjoyed their butter almond. It's hard to find that flavor anywhere else.\""
    j "\"嗯？哦，我一直很喜欢他们的奶油杏仁。在其他地方很难吃到那种味道。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:244
translate Schinese findtj_a9fa790e:

    # "TJ looks at me and I open my mouth to answer."
    "TJ看着我，我正准备开口回答。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:245
translate Schinese findtj_94c5faff:

    # "But for a moment, I draw a blank, the memories of Ray's hazy and blurred. My head is still buzzing."
    "但那一刻，我的脑海里一片空白，对雷氏甜品的记忆朦胧而模糊。我的头还在嗡嗡作响。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:246
translate Schinese findtj_7e30cfc5:

    # m "\"Oh, uh...Vanilla.\""
    m "\"哦，呃...香草冰淇淋。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:247
translate Schinese findtj_e9c1b202:

    # "I've been feeling pretty shitty ever since I'd had that talk with TJ by the river. I make a mental note to steal some of Jenna's aspirin before I go to bed."
    "自我和TJ在河边谈过之后，我就一直感觉很糟糕。我提醒自己睡前得去偷点儿Jenna的阿司匹林。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:248
translate Schinese findtj_8850c094:

    # c "\"Well...Flynn was right about one of us, at least.\""
    c "\"嗯...至少Flynn对我们其中一个人的判断是对的。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:250
translate Schinese findtj_deac8bbb:

    # t "\"Carl!\""
    t "\"Carl!\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:251
translate Schinese findtj_48d8e64e:

    # m "\"What's wrong with that? Everyone likes vanilla.\""
    m "\"有什么不对吗？大家都喜欢香草冰淇淋。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:252
translate Schinese findtj_aad63cab:

    # "I grin even though Carl's comment hurts me more than it should. He's just joking after all."
    "尽管Carl的话有些伤到我，但我还是笑了。他毕竟只是在开玩笑。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:253
translate Schinese findtj_dec9836e:

    # c "\"But I mean, who loves it, right?\""
    c "\"但我的意思是，又有谁钟爱香草冰淇淋呢，对吧？\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:254
translate Schinese findtj_4100826f:

    # "{i}...personality of a rock.{/i}"
    "{i}...像个石头一样毫无个性。{/i}"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:255
translate Schinese findtj_14be96cd:

    # t "\"I think it's a good answer, especially if you put toppings on it.\""
    t "\"我觉得这个回答很不错啊，如果再撒点配料就更好了。\""

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:258
translate Schinese findtj_4a364a8c:

    # "The buzzing picks up and I feel a dull pulse behind my eyes."
    "嗡嗡声越来越大，我能感觉到我的眼皮在跳。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:259
translate Schinese findtj_652d11c0:

    # "The three of them continue to talk amongst themselves as I lean my head back against the couch."
    "我把头靠在沙发上，而他们三个人还在继续交谈。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:261
translate Schinese findtj_5932e293:

    # "I close my eyes, trying to will away the pounding in my head."
    "我闭上眼睛，试图缓解头疼。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:266
translate Schinese findtj_6f28753f:

    # "I open my eyes. The room is dark. Jenna is in her bed, TJ is in his, Carl's wrapped in a blanket on the floor."
    "我睁开眼睛。房间里黑了下来。Jenna在她的床上，TJ也在他自己的床上，Carl则裹着毯子躺在地板上。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:267
translate Schinese findtj_cec8046e:

    # "I lurch for my camera bag, then look around wide-eyed."
    "我跌跌撞撞地拿起相机包，睁大眼睛四处张望。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:270
translate Schinese findtj_91f17ee9:

    # "I sit on the bed next to TJ and stare at the door..."
    "我坐在TJ旁边，盯着门看..."

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:276
translate Schinese findtj_5930a780:

    # "TJ stands at the edge of the lake, staring across to the other side."
    "TJ站在河边，望向对岸。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:277
translate Schinese findtj_5d6a0b86:

    # "He has one paw in his pocket, the other holding a beer."
    "他一只爪子揣在兜里，另一只手握着啤酒。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:278
translate Schinese findtj_e8883164:

    # "He takes a drink from it...TJ doesn't drink beer."
    "他喝了一口...TJ不会喝啤酒。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:279
translate Schinese findtj_ce8bde24:

    # "He pulls the tab off the top, then flicks it towards the lake."
    "他把拉环扯了下来，径直甩向湖面。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:280
translate Schinese findtj_77e581d4:

    # "It whizzes like a weed cutter, skipping across the water and kicking up spray."
    "拉环像割草机一般嗖嗖地掠过水面，溅起水花。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:281
translate Schinese findtj_7700b65a:

    # "Suddenly, his ears snap up and he sees something I don't."
    "突然，他竖起耳朵，看见了 我所没看见的东西。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:282
translate Schinese findtj_a831f106:

    # "He turns and starts to run."
    "他转身就跑。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:283
translate Schinese findtj_53966ae7:

    # "He's at a dead sprint when his leg snaps out from under him and he falls to the rocks, beer splashing everywhere."
    "他正全速冲刺，突然被绊倒了，摔在岩石上，啤酒溅得满地都是。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:284
translate Schinese findtj_afb80956:

    # "A chain is pulled taut from the lake, connected to his ankle."
    "一条锁链紧咬着他的脚踝，末端牢牢沉在湖水中。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:285
translate Schinese findtj_04865ee1:

    # "I get up, wanting to help, but I can't."
    "我站起身来想去帮忙，但我办不到。"

# game/Monday-TJ.rpy:286
translate Schinese findtj_9475a707:

    # "I look down, my wrist and ankle chained..."
    "我朝身下看去，发现自己的手腕和脚踝被锁链缠绕..."

